Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Reality slips far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Fiction comes alive,we start to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope is no more ,behind a closed door
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}As we drift away from where we were before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope and hopelessness become one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:37.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's all meaningless ,we've already begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:39.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}yup, we are all one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Never opposites,we play the same game
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Walk the thin line between hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:44.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Running from the truth,but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Told so many lies, I dunno if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Only one life to live,so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Heads or tails,do you even know the side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Doesn't really matter if it's on the same coin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you wanna achieve you gotta believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:56.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's on right now, here's the door here's the key
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:59.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2}The search is so very long, we let it fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:03.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}There's a ray of hope beyond despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:08.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Move on, look for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}In this world　　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:14.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Slip through the confusion, find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:18.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Beat the twisted evil things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:22.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Just do it, go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:25.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Never...
